title: War of the Roses: Get This Tattoo or We're Done
description: Jessica caught Dylan cheating before when she found out he wasn't going to lunch with his mom like he said.  So now she wants him to get something tattooed on his chest and if he doesn't do it, she thinks he's still cheating.
